OL,3,CVincent Tan responds to Cardiff City
OL,4,Cfans calls for meeting, after
OL,5,Crelegation
OL,7,FCardiff City's owner Vincent Tan has
OL,8,Fhit back at criticism from the club's
OL,9,Fsupporters following their relegation
OL,10,Fto League One.
OL,12,FAfter Saturday's draw to West Bromwich
OL,13,FAlbion that sealed their demotion,
OL,14,Fthere were chants of "Vincent Tan, get
OL,15,Fout of our club" outside the stadium,
OL,16,Fand the Supporter's Trust demanded an
OL,17,Furgent meeting with him.
