OL,3,CVincent Tan responds to Cardiff City
OL,4,Cfans calls for meeting, after
OL,5,Crelegation
OL,7,FHis response is his first message to
OL,8,Fsupporters posted on the official
OL,9,FCardiff City website since they
OL,10,Fsecured promotion to the Premier
OL,11,FLeague for the 2018/2019 season.
OL,13,FAlthough he did not explicitly grant
OL,14,Ftheir wish for a meeting, he
OL,15,Facknowledged the letter, saying "We
OL,16,Fhear your words and I share your hurt
OL,17,Fand frustration.
OL,19,F"Not all decisions when it comes to
OL,20,Fthe First Team have worked as I had
OL,21,Fhoped for us.
