OL,3,CVincent Tan responds to Cardiff City
OL,4,Cfans calls for meeting, after
OL,5,Crelegation
OL,7,F"To lose our place in the Championship
OL,8,Fis upsetting. The important thing is
OL,9,Fthat we regain it at the earliest
OL,10,Fopportunity and I would like to take
OL,11,Fthis chance to tell you that I am
OL,12,Fcommitted to getting us back.
