OL,3,CVincent Tan responds to Cardiff City
OL,4,Cfans calls for meeting, after
OL,5,Crelegation
OL,7,FHe outlined the steps being taken to
OL,8,Fimprove results at the club and secure
OL,9,Fpromotion, saying "A period of review
OL,10,Fis being undertaken; a permanent
OL,11,Fmanager and management team will be
OL,12,Fappointed in the coming weeks. As a
OL,13,Fpoint of developing strategy, our
OL,14,FBoard of Directors have begun internal
OL,15,Fdiscussions with executive management
OL,16,Fand staff to strategise and plan for
OL,17,Fthe summer and new season."
OL,19,FHe also hit back at criticism from
OL,20,Fsome Cardiff fans that he is
OL,21,Fdisinterested in the club.
OL,1,W~s1{$~k4{$k7                    G4/15
