OL,3,CVincent Tan responds to Cardiff City
OL,4,Cfans calls for meeting, after
OL,5,Crelegation
OL,7,F"To say I don't care is wrong and I
OL,8,Fstrongly push back on that. I watch
OL,9,Fevery game and speak to the Board and
OL,10,Fmanager before and after each one. My
OL,11,Ffamily will tell you: I kick every
OL,12,Fball!
OL,14,F"We have enjoyed good times together.
OL,15,FI can tell all Cardiff City supporters
OL,16,Fthat it is my intention to support
OL,17,Fcorrecting the situation we find
OL,18,Fourselves in. I want us to all pull in
OL,19,Fthe same direction.
OL,1,W~s1{$~k4{$k7                    G5/15
