OL,3,CVincent Tan responds to Cardiff City
OL,4,Cfans calls for meeting, after
OL,5,Crelegation
OL,7,F"I will make every effort to be in
OL,8,FCardiff at the next opportunity that
OL,9,Fmy scheduling allows. I am sorry that
OL,10,Fwe are where we are this summer. It is
OL,11,Fnow time to rebuild."
OL,13,FThe last time Tan visited the Cardiff
OL,14,FCity Stadium was in December 2023.
