OL,7,FCardiff were playing Premier League
OL,8,Ffootball in 2019, but Malaysian
OL,9,Fbusinessman Vincent Tan's turbulent 15-
OL,10,Fyear ownership of the club has seen 16
OL,11,Fdifferent managers, including
OL,12,Fcaretaker appointments, and eight in
OL,13,Fthe last four years.
OL,15,FIn its statement, the Supporter's
OL,16,FTrust blasted the running of the club.
