OL,3,CVincent Tan responds to Cardiff City
OL,4,Cfans calls for meeting, after
OL,5,Crelegation
OL,7,F"Relegation has been coming since the
OL,8,F2021-22 season and the failure to
OL,9,Faddress fundamental required changes
OL,10,Ffrom the top down has now come home to
OL,11,Froost.
OL,13,F"Unless these matters are tackled
OL,14,Furgently, the downward spiral on and
OL,15,Foff the field will continue and fan
OL,16,Fsupport will continue to drift away at
OL,17,Fan even faster rate than it has
OL,18,Falready."
