OL,8,Fappointment of a club board member
OL,9,Fwith specialist football knowledge and
OL,10,Fexperience, while it dubs the
OL,11,Fappointment of Omer Riza a "mistake...
OL,12,Fwhen there many experienced managers
OL,13,Favailable to recruit", and calls for
OL,14,Fan experienced manager for the League
OL,15,FOne campaign next season.
