OL,7,FThe trust added: "We are also
OL,8,Fdisappointed that Vincent Tan has made
OL,9,Fonly minimal and very infrequent
OL,10,Fcontact with the club fans to discuss
OL,11,Fissues and listen to fans views and
OL,12,Fconcerns. There has therefore been
OL,13,Fvirtually no opportunity for fans to
OL,14,Fspeak to the person who appears to be
OL,15,Fthe sole decision-maker on key issues
OL,16,Fat the club.
