OL,3,CVincent Tan responds to Cardiff City
OL,4,Cfans calls for meeting, after
OL,5,Crelegation
OL,7,F"As a matter of urgency we are
OL,8,Frequesting a meeting between Vincent
OL,9,FTan and the elected fan bodies to
OL,10,Fdiscuss the failings which have
OL,11,Fculminated in our relegation to hear
OL,12,Fwhat fundamental changes are going to
OL,13,Fbe put in place throughout the club
OL,14,Ffrom top to bottom to avoid further
OL,15,Ffailings in future.
