OL,7,FIt comes after interim manager Aaron
OL,8,FRamsey said he was "gutted" over
OL,9,FCardiff's relegation from the
OL,10,FChampionship as the "miracle ending"
OL,11,Fhe craved at his boyhood club turned
OL,12,Fto disaster.
OL,14,FRamsey, the Wales captain currently
OL,15,Fsidelined by injury, returned to his
OL,16,Ffirst club two summers ago after
OL,17,Fplaying for Arsenal and Juventus and
OL,18,Fspoke about helping Cardiff back to
OL,19,Fthe Premier League.
