OL,7,FBut Saturday's 0-0 draw at home to
OL,8,FWest Brom confirmed Cardiff will spend
OL,9,Fnext season in the third tier of
OL,10,FEnglish football for the first time
OL,11,Fsince 2003.
OL,13,F"I'm gutted, I'm a fan as well and sad
OL,14,Fto see this club going down," said
OL,15,FRamsey, who was put in caretaker
OL,16,Fcharge with three games left following
OL,17,Fthe sacking of Omer Riza.
OL,19,F"The fans have had a difficult time
OL,20,Fthis season and I really feel for
OL,21,Fthem. I know how they're feeling.
