OL,3,CVincent Tan responds to Cardiff City
OL,4,Cfans calls for meeting, after
OL,5,Crelegation
OL,7,F"But also I want to say I'm proud of
OL,8,Fthe last couple of performances. The
OL,9,Flevel of effort the players have put
OL,10,Fin and the information they've taken
OL,11,Fon was evident."
OL,13,FRiza himself only took charge in
OL,14,FSeptember after Cardiff had picked up
OL,15,Fone point from their first seven games
OL,16,Funder Erol Bulut.
OL,18,FAsked where the season had gone wrong,
OL,19,FRamsey said: "I don't know. We need to
OL,20,Fhave a bit of time to think and
OL,21,Freflect on that.
